But for me, I will wait on Jehovah;
I will look for the God of my strength;
In the darkness Jehovah will shine like a light;
Let my enemies no more rejoice.
For I fall, but then I will rise up;
Praise the Lord, Who's the strength of my heart;
So for me, I will wait on the Lord Jesus Christ;
And in Christ I will rise up again.
